    "comment": "Rationale: Fig.2: Electrophysiological Tag of NMDA-R Allows Monitoring of Functional Insertion of Recombinant Receptor into Synapses.. Experimental description: - Species of the over-expressed protein is not stated in the paper. Authors were contacted (rmalinow@ucsd.edu, barria@uw.edu, dd 24/11/2017). Authors answered:\n\n\"HI,\nYes, in both papers (Barria & Malinow, Neuron 2002 and 2005) the receptors are from rat.\nThe original clones were obtained from Nakanishi's lab or Mishina's lab via Yasunori Hayashi.\nAt some point I fully sequenced them and they are a match with the rat sequence deposited in NCBI\n\nCheers\nAndres\"",
